* Method:			GetOAuth
* Purpose:			Gets a SaslMechanismOAuth2 object
* Author:			Doug Hennig, adapted from code written by Matthew Olson
* Last revision:	03/07/2022
* Parameters:		none
* Returns:			a MailKit.Security.SaslMechanismOAuth2 object or NULL if
